%20it%3A%20you%20know%20you%20did%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20criticism%20aimed%20at%20the%20Republican%20politicians%20who%20voted%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20sharp%20words%20for%20Trump's%20bill%20come%20just%20days%20after%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-gift-elon-musk-key-white-house-doge-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eofficially%20left%20his%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20de%20facto%20head%20of%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDOGE%20office%2C%20ending%20his%20formal%20work%20at%20the%20White%20House.%20In%20recent%20weeks%2C%20both%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20have%20looked%20to%20assure%20the%20public%20that%20their%20relationship%20remains%20intact%2C%20even%20if%20they%20disagree%20on%20some%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20press%20secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20said%20in%20a%20briefing%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20President%20already%20knew%20where%20Musk%20stood%20on%20the%20spending%20bill%20and%20that%20the%20Tesla%20CEO's%20recent%20comments%20criticizing%20it%20wouldn't%20change%20Trump's%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-beautiful-bill-medicaid-taxes-maga-accounts-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20champions%20Trump's%20agenda%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20cuts%20to%20Medicaid%20and%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20tax%20cuts%20that%20the%20president%20signed%20into%20law%20during%20his%20first%20term%20in%202017.%20It%20also%20includes%20administration%20priorities%2C%20including%20removing%20taxes%20on%20tips%20and%20overtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20regard%20to%20the%20companies%20Musk%20leads%2C%20the%20bill%20could%20have%20a%20mixed%20impact.%20While%20Tesla%20stands%20to%20potentially%20lose%2C%20companies%20like%20SpaceX%20and%20xAI%20may%20benefit%20from%20the%20president's%20massive%20spending%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283890d8a-59ff-4ba8-a61c-da55bd93660e%5C%22%3ETesla's%20credits%20threatened%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20as%20written%2C%20makes%20big%20changes%20to%20the%20Biden-era%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-state-electric-car-vehicle-tax-credits-rebates-qualify%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEV%20tax%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20aim%20to%20encourage%20more%20Americans%20to%20buy%20electric%20vehicles.%20It%20would%20largely%20phase%20out%20the%20clean%20vehicle%20credit%2C%20which%20lets%20people%20buying%20a%20new%20EV%20claim%20up%20to%20%247%2C500%2C%20and%20up%20to%20%244%2C000%20for%20used-EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20vehicles%20would%20no%20longer%20qualify%20for%20the%20tax%20credit%20if%20the%20automaker%20sold%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20previously%20qualifying%20EVs%20between%20December%2031%2C%202009%2C%20and%20December%2031%2C%202025%2C%20if%20the%20bill%20became%20law.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-history-founders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20delivered%20more%20than%20336%2C000%20vehicles%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20previously%20said%20that%20eliminating%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%20would%20devastate%20Tesla's%20competitors%20and%20impact%20the%20automaker%20as%20well.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20move%20would%20probably%20help%20Tesla%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20don't%20seem%20sold%20on%20Musk's%20rationale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeth%20Goldstein%2C%20an%20equity%20strategist%20at%20Morningstar%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20expedited%20elimination%20of%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20area%20that%20could%20impact%20Tesla.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%20have%20increased%20long%20range%20EV%20choices%20at%20similar%20price%20points%20as%20Tesla%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20on%20Tesla%20to%20make%20the%20case%20for%20consumers%20to%20even%20slightly%20pay%20up%20today%20versus%20some%20other%20EVs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldstein%20said%20that%20tax%20credit%20elimination%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20decrease%20in%20sales%20volume%2C%20which%20the%20automaker%20has%20already%20been%20struggling%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20analyst%20Ryan%20Brinkman%20wrote%20in%20an%20investor%20note%20that%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%2C%26quot%3B%20combined%20with%20other%20proposed%20legislation%2C%20including%20ending%20the%20California%20Air%20Resources%20Board%20Program%2C%20threatens%20over%20half%20of%20Tesla's%202025%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrinkman%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%20that%20the%20%247%2C500%20consumer%20tax%20made%20up%2019%25%20of%20Tesla's%202024%20earnings%20before%20interest%20and%20tax%2C%20and%20could%20result%20in%20a%20potential%20%241.2%20billion%20headwind.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20automaker%20could%20face%20a%20%242%20billion%20headwind%20from%20the%20removal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-elon-musk-supports-donald-trump-election-save-tesla-disaster-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECARB%20ZEV%3C%2Fa%3E%20credit%20sales%2C%20which%20encourage%20the%20sales%20of%20zero-emission%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20betting%20big%20on%20AI%20and%20robotics%20as%20it%20pushes%20to%20reach%20full%20autonomy%2C%20in%20part%20through%20its%20upcoming%20robotaxi%20service%2C%20efforts%20that%20Musk%20has%20said%20are%20key%20to%20growing%20the%20company's%20valuation.%20However%2C%20Brinkman%20said%20that%20any%20material%20benefit%20from%20Tesla's%20autonomous%20robotaxi%20business%20is%20years%20away%2C%20while%20the%20headwind%20from%20EV%20subsidy%20removal%20would%20likely%20hit%20the%20automaker%20in%202025%20and%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20estimates%20to%20come%20down%20as%20the%20impact%20of%20Trump%20Administration%20EV%20subsidy%20removal%20becomes%20clearer%2C%26quot%3B%20Brinkman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldstein%20said%20that%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20tax%20credit%20could%20%26quot%3Baccelerate%26quot%3B%20Tesla's%20transition%20to%20an%20AI%20and%20robotics%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20possible%20that%20the%20expiration%20of%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%20on%20Tesla%20vehicles%20could%20spur%20some%20short-term%20demand%20from%20buyers%20looking%20to%20purchase%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20EVs%20before%20the%20window%20closes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20spending%20bill%20wouldn't%20only%20change%20existing%20taxes%20and%20fees.%20Under%20its%20current%20language%2C%20it%20would%20also%20impose%20a%20%24250%20yearly%20fee%20for%20EV%20drivers%20through%20the%20Federal%20Highway%20Administration%2C%20and%20a%20%24100%20yearly%20fee%20for%20hybrid%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20written%2C%20the%20bill%20also%20scraps%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Flpo%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloan%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Tesla%20utilized%20in%202010%2C%20long%20before%20Trump%20even%20entered%20the%20political%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spending%20bill%20also%20threatens%20Tesla's%20energy%20business%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteslas-biggest-growth-business-q3-energy-storage-batteries-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20has%20said%20is%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20like%20wildfire%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20ending%20energy%20tax%20credits.%20The%20automaker's%20energy%20generation%20and%20storage%20business%2C%20which%20includes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteslas-biggest-growth-business-q3-energy-storage-batteries-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETesla's%20Megapack%20and%20Powerwall%20battery%20systems%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20brought%20in%20%242.73%20billion%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20a%2067%25%20increase%20from%20the%20year%20prior.%3C