med%20very%20well%20in%20all%20our%20tests%2C%20from%20comfort%20to%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20silk%20is%20noticeably%20thick%20and%20high-quality%2C%20and%20is%20resistant%20to%20tearing.%20I%20loved%20the%20way%20it%20felt%20against%20my%20skin%20and%20hair.%20It's%20incredibly%20comfortable%20to%20sleep%20on%2C%20and%20I%20found%20myself%20gravitating%20toward%20it%20when%20I%20wasn't%20actively%20testing%20another%20product.%20Even%20now%2C%20after%20the%20testing%20period%20is%20over%2C%20you%20can%20find%20the%20Lilysilk%20pillowcase%20on%20my%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20durability%2C%20I%20scratched%20the%20pillowcase%20with%20my%20fingernails%2050%20times%20to%20simulate%20pet%20scratching%20or%20an%20earring%20catching%20in%20your%20pillowcase%2C%20I%20noticed%20no%20loose%20threads%20or%20pilling.%20It%20also%20performed%20well%20in%20cooling%20tests%2C%20only%20increasing%20in%20temperature%20by%20about%202.2%20degrees%20after%20lying%20on%20it%20for%20two%20minutes.%20Subjectively%2C%20I%20never%20once%20woke%20up%20feeling%20overheated%20when%20using%20this%20pillowcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Lilysilk%20pillowcase%20on%20floral%20sheets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f19ed6ffb6822ec61f680%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELilysilk's%20silk%20pillowcase%20was%20my%20favorite%20out%20of%20all%20pillowcases%20I%20tried%2C%20performing%20excellently%20in%20all%20of%20my%20tests.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20that%20the%20pillowcase%20wrinkles%20easily%2C%20especially%20immediately%20after%20removing%20it%20from%20its%20packaging%20and%20washing.%20The%20washing%20process%20is%20more%20tedious%20than%20that%20of%20other%20pillowcases%20in%20our%20guide.%20While%20some%20silk%20pillowcases%20can%20be%20machine%20washed%20on%20delicate%2C%20the%20Lilysilk%20pillowcase%20is%20hand-wash%20only.%20That%20said%2C%20it%20held%20up%20well%20to%20handwashing.%20All%20saliva%20stains%20(gross%2C%20I%20know)%20were%20completely%20gone%20after%20hand%20washing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELilysilk's%20silk%20pillowcase%20comes%20in%20standard%2C%20queen%2C%20and%20king%20sizes.%20You%20choose%20from%20eight%20colors%2C%20from%20a%20classic%20black%20to%20a%20sunny%20butter%20yellow.%20Add%20a%20personal%20flair%20to%20your%20silk%20pillowcase%20with%20a%20monogram%20in%20the%20top-right%20corner.%20For%20%2420%2C%20you%20can%20embroider%20up%20to%2010%20characters.%20Non-customized%20items%20can%20be%20returned%20within%20100%20days%20of%20use%2C%20although%20you'll%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20return%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244d935ad-8801-469d-b798-4acc806102b9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3ESilk%20is%20a%20pricey%20material%2C%20making%20finding%20a%20budget%20silk%20pillowcase%20difficult.%20Many%20companies%20remedy%20the%20expense%20by%20blending%20silk%20with%20a%20cheaper%20material%2C%20like%20cotton%2C%20or%20using%20silk%20on%20only%20one%20side%20of%20the%20pillowcase.%20But%20our%20budget%20pick%2C%20the%20Bedsure%20Mulberry%20Silk%20Pillowcase%2C%20is%20made%20entirely%20with%20100%25%2019-momme%20mulberry%20silk%20and%20costs%20under%20%2430%20on%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20unboxed%20it%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20with%20its%20quality.%20I%20had%20expected%20a%20cheaper%20feel%2C%20but%20Bedsure's%20pillowcase%20compared%20well%20to%20pillowcases%20double%20the%20price.%20It's%20not%20the%20thickest%20silk%2C%20but%20it's%20remarkably%20smooth.%20I%20saw%20a%20noticeable%20difference%20in%20my%20skin%20and%20hair%20when%20I%20used%20this%20silk%20pillowcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20light%20pink%20Bedsure%20silk%20pillowcase%20on%20floral%20sheets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f1a9bca50259add4d8519%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bedsure%20Mulberry%20Silk%20Pillowcase%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20silk%20pillowcases%20you%20can%20buy%20on%20a%20budget.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20pillow%20pet%20peeves%20is%20when%20a%20pillow%20shifts%20in%20its%20pillowcase.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20loved%20the%20hidden%20zipper%20in%20this%20pillowcase.%20The%20pillowcase%20fit%20the%20pillow%20well%2C%20and%20the%20zipper%20kept%20everything%20in%20place.%20I%20never%20felt%20the%20zipper%20when%20I%20was%20sleeping%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20care%20and%20abrasion%20testing%2C%20this%20isn't%20the%20most%20durable%20option.%20This%20pillowcase%20stained%20easily%2C%20with%20noticeable%20saliva%20stains%20against%20the%20light%20pink%20color.%20Bedsure's%20silk%20pillowcase%20is%20handwash%20only%2C%20and%20even%20when%20I%20scrubbed%20at%20the%20stains%20per%20the%20care%20instructions%2C%20they%20remained.%20The%20stains%20aren't%20as%20pronounced%20now%2C%20but%20they%20still%20stand%20out%20on%20the%20pillowcase.%20There%20were%20also%20several%20loose%20threads%20after%20abrasion%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBedsure's%20silk%20pillowcase%20also%20has%20subpar%20cooling.%20It%20started%20at%2073.2%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20before%20rising%20to%2076.2%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20after%20I%20lay%20on%20it%2C%20which%20was%20above%20the%20average%20starting%20and%20testing%20temperatures.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20heat%20dissipated%20to%20the%20original%20temperature%20after%20two%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBedsure%20offers%2030-day%20returns%20for%20their%20products%2C%20but%20you'll%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20%249.99%20return%20fee%20if%20your%20item%20isn't%20defective%20when%20you%20buy%20directly%20from%20their%20website.%20On%20Amazon%2C%20you%20can%20return%20your%20pillowcase%20within%2030%20days%20for%20free.%20The%20Mulberry%20Silk%20Pillowcase%20is%20sold%20in%20three%20sizes%20and%20eight%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228b8f5cc-3f83-430b-81f1-070700f72db8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20cooling%5C%22%3EBest%20cooling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20cooling%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20I%20find%20that%20the%20heat%20from%20my%20face%20gets%20trapped%20in%20my%20pillowcase%2C%20which%20leaves%20me%20flipping%20my%20pillow%20over%20to%20find%20the%20cool%20side.%20I%20never%20had%20that%20issue%20when%20testing%20the%20Celestial%20Silk%2025-Momme%20Mulberry%20Silk%20Pillowcase.%20The%20fabric%20stayed%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20easily%20dissipating%20my%20body%20heat%20for%20a%20comfortable%20night's%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Celestial%20Silk%20pillowcase%20wasn't%20the%20objectively%20most%20cooling%20pillowcase%20we%20tried%E2%80%94%20that%20title%20goes%20to%20the%20Slip%20Silk%20Pillowcase%2C%20our%20best%20for%20skin%20and%20hair%20pick%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20still%20outstanding%20in%20our%20cooling%20tests.%20Plus%2C%20it%20subjectively%20felt%20the%20coolest%20throughout%20the%20testing%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hot%20pink%20Celestial%20Silk%20pillowcase%20on%20floral%20sheets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f1affca50259add4d8531%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelestial%20Silk's%20pillowcase%20comes%20wrapped%20in%20tissue%20paper%20and%20box%2C%20making%20it%20an%20an%20excellent%20giftable%20option.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20impressed%20with%20this%20pillowcase's%20ease%20of%20cleaning.%20While%20other%20picks%20in%20our%20guide%20are%20handwash%20only%2C%20the%20Celestial%20Silk%20is%20machine%20washable.%20Just%20toss%20it%20in%20a%20delicates%20bag%2C%20wash%20on%20a%20cold%20cycle%2C%20and%20then%20hang%20to%20air%20dry.%20The%20pillow%20looked%20and%20felt%20good%20as%20new%20after%20washing%20and%20drying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20unboxing%20the%20pillowcase%2C%20I%20did%20notice%20some%20loose%20threads%20in%20the%20seam%2C%20but%20I%20could%20remove%20them%20without%20damaging%20it.%20Celestial%20Silk%20also%20only%20offers%2030-day%20returns%20for%20unused%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Celestial%20Silk%2025-momme%20pillowcase%20is%20available%20in%2019%20colors%20and%20patterns.%20I%20tried%20the%20hot%20pink%20and%20loved%20the%20splash%20of%20vibrant%20color%20it%20brought%20to%20my%20room%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20buy%20it%20in%20neutral%20tones%20or%20designs%20like%20floral%20or%20marble.%20It's%20available%20in%20standard%2C%20queen%2C%20and%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d086b0b-80cf-4d87-bd80-66ef0560fc6b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20skin%20and%20hair%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20skin%20and%20hair%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20skin%20and%20hair%5C%22%3EMy%20skin%20and%20hair%20can%20be%20temperamental.%20I%20have%20dry%2C%20sensitive%20skin%20that's%20prone%20to%20acne%20and%20wavy-curly%20hair%20that%20loves%20to%20frizz%20no%20matter%20the%20time%20of%20year.%20Like%20many%20other%20people%20on%20their%20curly%20hair%20journey%2C%20I've%20heard%20silk%20combats%20bedhead%20for%20smoother%20hair.%20After%20testing%20almost%20a%20dozen%20silk%20pillowcases%2C%20I%20found%20that%20Slip's%20Silk%20Pillowcase%20is%20the%20best%20for%20skin%20and%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20sleep%20with%20a%20satin%20bonnet%20to%20protect%20my%20hair%2C%20so%20I%20was%20nervous%20to%20sleep%20without%20one%20while%20testing%20silk%20pillowcases.%20Usually%2C%20sleeping%20on%20a%20cotton%20pillowcase%20completely%20ruins%20my%20curl%20structure%20and%20leaves%20my%20hair%20frizzy%20and%20poofy%20the%20next%20day.%20With%20Slip's%20pillowcase%2C%20though%2C%20my%20curls%20looked%20soft%20and%20bouncy%2C%20even%20without%20a%20satin%20bonnet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20Slip%20pillowcase%20on%20floral%20sheets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f1b586ffb6822ec61f6ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tried%20Slip's%20black%20pillowcase%2C%20but%20they%20have%20a%20range%20of%20fun%20designs%20as%20well.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20benefits%20in%20my%20skin%2C%20too.%20I%20noticed%20a%20considerable%20reduction%20in%20my%20skin's%20redness%20and%20didn't%20have%20as%20many%20breakouts.%20My%20skin%20felt%20plump%20and%20moisturized%20%E2%80%94%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20tight%2C%20dry%20skin%20I%20usually%20have%20after%20waking%20up%20on%20a%20cotton%20pillowcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20for%20skin%20and%20hair%20come%20from%20the%20pillowcase's%20unbelievably%20smooth%20texture.%20This%20pillowcase%20was%2C%20by%20far%2C%20the%20softest%20and%20smoothest%20silk%20pillowcase%20I%20tried.%20There%20was%20little%20friction%20between%20my%20head%20and%20the%20pillow.%20Plus%2C%20it%20performed%20best%20in%20our%20cooling%20tests%2C%20so%20it's%20great%20for%20hot%20sleepers%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quality%20comes%20at%20a%20high%20price%20tag%2C%20though.%20A%20queen-size%20pillowcase%20will%20cost%20you%20%24105.%20It's%20also%20cumbersome%20to%20wash%20since%20Slip%20recommends%20a%20specific%20pH-neutral%20detergent%20to%20clean%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlip's%20silk%20pillowcases%2C%20which%20are%20sold%20in%20queen%20and%20king%20sizes%2C%20are%20also%20available%20with%20an%20envelope%20enclosure.%20Slip%20consistently%20releases%20limited-edition%20colors%20and%20patterns%E2%80%94I%20especially%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slip.com%2Fcollections%2Fqueen-pillowcases%2Fproducts%2Fsunshade-queen-zippered-pillowcase-with-scalloped-edge%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20scalloped%20edge%20and%20vibrant%20pink%20and%20red%20stripes%20on%20this%20pillowcase%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228fc58a55-daf9-49a1-bb3c-bb580b5f3d96%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20organic%5C%22%3EBest%20organic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20for%20silk%20to%20be%20considered%20organic%20differs%20from%20that%20of%20other%20materials%20since%20silk%20is%20made%20from%20the%20cocoons%20of%20silkworms.%20To%20be%20considered%20organic%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobal-standard.org%2Fthe-standard%2Fgots-key-features%2Forganic-fibres%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20fibers%20must%20be%20made%20using%20sustainable%20practices%20and%20be%20chemical%20and%20GMO-free.%3C%2Fa%3E%20For%20silk%2C%20the%20silkworms%20must%20only%20eat%20organic%20plant%20matter%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobal-standard.org%2Fcertification-and-labelling%2Fwho-needs-to-be-certified%2Ffirst-processing-stages%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecocoons%20must%20be%20boiled%20and%20washed.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20these%20requirements%2C%20organic%20silk%20is%20difficult%20to%20find%2C%20so%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20try%20Clementine's%20Organic%2022-momme%20Silk%20Pillowcase.%20I%20attest%2C%20it's%20a%20hidden%20gem.%20Not%20only%20did%20I%20sleep%20easy%20knowing%20that%20the%20pillowcase%20was%20GOTS-certified%20organic%2C%20but%20I%20loved%20this%20pillowcase's%20feel.%20It%20had%20the%20thickest%20silk%20of%20all%20the%20pillowcases%20I%20tested.%20It%20was%20also%20ridiculously%20soft%2C%20with%20a%20feel%20similar%20to%20a%20bamboo%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20lavender%20Clementine%20organic%20silk%20pillowcase%20on%20floral%20sheets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f1bd76ffb6822ec61f6e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClementine's%20Organic%20Silk%20Pillowcase%20is%20a%20hidden%20gem.%20I%20loved%20the%20feel%20of%20its%20organic%20materials.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20envelope%20enclosure%20did%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20slipping%20off%20at%20night%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20quick%20fix%20in%20the%20morning.%20Even%20the%20packaging%20is%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20your%20pillowcase%20comes%20in%20a%20cotton%20cover%20in%20a%20thick%2C%20magnetic%20cardboard%20box.%20It'd%20make%20an%20ideal%20gift%20for%20the%20eco-conscious%20friend.%20It%20comes%20in%20seven%20colors%2C%20including%20a%20luxe%20gold%2C%20and%20queen%20and%20king%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%20for%20the%20quality%20and%20certification%2C%20this%20is%20an%20expensive%20pillowcase.%20You%20can%20also%20only%20return%20your%20pillowcase%20if%20unused%20within%2030%20days%2C%20so%20it's%20more%20of%20a%20risk%20if%20you%20decide%20you%20don't%20like%20it.%20I%20also%20noticed%20torn%20threads%20in%20the%20stitching%20and%20pillow%20during%20abrasion%20testing%3B%20it%20sustained%20the%20most%20damage%20of%20all%20the%20pillowcases%20I%20tested.%20You'll%20have%20to%20be%20extra%20careful%20when%20using%20this%20pillowcase%20and%20keep%20it%20away%20from%20pets%20and%20their%20claws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4839d64-554f-4ba4-86d2-6c1d89a5a4c0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20mulberry%5C%22%3EBest%20mulberry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20mulberry%5C%22%3EIn%20my%20interview%20with%20Walker%2C%20she%20said%20that%20mulberry%20silk%20is%20produced%20by%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20moth%20caterpillar.%20%26quot%3B'Mulberry%20silk'%20refers%20to%20silk%20produced%20by%20the%20Bombyx%20mori%20silk%20moth%2C%20a%20domesticated%20insect.%20T