es%20to%20rise.%20%E2%80%9CParents%20who%20once%20hesitated%20to%20send%20their%20children%20now%20feel%20confident%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Patil.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stigma%20around%20rural%20government%20schools%20is%20fading.%20This%20building%20gave%20us%20that%20credibility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T122803.296-1748501901.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20in%20the%20morning%20assembly%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T122803.296-1748501901.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T122803.296-1748501901-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T122803.296-1748501901-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T122803.296-1748501901-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-29T122803.296-1748501901-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440883%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20design%20of%20the%20school%20has%20brought%20in%20confidence%20among%20the%20students%20and%20teachers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20transformation%20has%20also%20been%20officially%20recognised.%20Saraswati%20Vidyalaya%20recently%20received%20third%20prize%20in%20a%20statewide%20competition%20organised%20under%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20school%20excellence%20initiative%2C%20winning%20Rs%201%20lakh%20and%20earning